            <h1>How to Get Here</h1>
<p>We're easy to drive to and there's plenty of parking when you get here! Just follow Hazeldean Road or Eagleson Road. You can't miss Hazeldean Mall, we're located on the corner of Eagleson and Hazeldean Road.</p>
<h2>Public Transit </h2>
<p>Hazeldean Mall is serviced by OC Transpo bus service. Many main routes stop at the mall. Visit <a href="//www.octranspo.com" target="_blank">octranspo.com</a> for bus maps and schedules. </p>
